tps://images.food52.com/HgNEB5gLNOa1wdVmIHJe4R3HpxY=/964x964/filters:format(webp)/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg, https://images.food52.com/_R8zx_jHZAgImVeoHTp4hXOG5dY=/1928x1928/filters:format(webp)/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/jOnHY7N5ZpZD_wbRrl-JsOoMGVE=/964x964/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg, https://images.food52.com/MuQm0Fb78azBc4kiamRjl6Ni-mU=/1928x1928/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/ePIHb-jDhmEvunQId6TVCVlrGTs=/768x768/filters:format(webp)/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg, https://images.food52.com/YnoX-LZbiqmjWAewL_gYH9w1ok4=/1536x1536/filters:format(webp)/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 500px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/ynZQ-FPzs90ecEN_GiylXQlbmc0=/768x768/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg, https://images.food52.com/dlULO_5qoudSUQ4XfSGpl102EIA=/1536x1536/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/mCRbbbo5-DGRA5kBZ1JWonAO1hc=/375x375/filters:format(webp)/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg, https://images.food52.com/pOAKnVhGqpXD9xG8RXqTKTh4Rzw=/750x750/filters:format(webp)/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/pR93y3XISs6sbMtTPVSrOvG3bPs=/375x375/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg, https://images.food52.com/Lf8BzccKzQtl0_n2YpflJXrPQ9s=/750x750/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"964\" height=\"964\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/pR93y3XISs6sbMtTPVSrOvG3bPs=/375x375/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg, https://images.food52.com/Lf8BzccKzQtl0_n2YpflJXrPQ9s=/750x750/763141e8-462e-40ec-b3be-825e58ddf2b5--image1_3-.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003ch2\u003e6: Doting on my dog\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eHere’s our dog Fiver, who turned 4 last week. I talk to her. She doesn’t understand me, but she pretends to be interested.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eSee you next week!\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eAmanda\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \n\n\n  \n\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n            \n\n\n\n            \n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n\n    \u003cp\u003e\n      Before starting Food52 with Merrill, I was a food writer and editor at the New York Times. I\u0026#39;ve written several books, including \u0026#34;Cooking for Mr. Latte\u0026#34; and \u0026#34;The Essential New York Times Cookbook.\u0026#34; I played myself in \u0026#34;Julie \u0026amp; Julia\u0026#34; -- hope you didn\u0026#39;t blink, or you may have missed the scene! I live in Brooklyn with my husband, Tad, and twins, Walker and Addison.\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003ePopular on Food52\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
